# OpenWiki documentation is committed to the repo on purpose.
#
# These files are owned by `openwiki --update`
# (https://github.com/langchain-ai/openwiki) and refreshed nightly by
# `.github/workflows/openwiki-update.yml`. The workflow opens a PR with
# the updated files; humans review and merge.
#
# Do not hand-edit the generated `.md` files unless you are absolutely
# sure. If you need to influence the content, change the project source
# code or `openwiki/quickstart.md`, then run `openwiki --update` and
# commit the diff.
#
# This .gitignore intentionally has no rules. It exists only so that
# `openwiki --init` does not accidentally stash files here.